	2.	You may Deploy TEN-VAD solely to create and enable deployment of your Application(s), solely for your benefit and the benefit of your direct End Users. If you prefer, you may include the following notice in your Application documentation:
“Powered by TEN-VAD.”
	3.	Derivative Works of TEN-VAD remain subject to this Open Source License.
	4.	“End Users” refers to the end-users of your Application(s) who access TEN-VAD solely as needed to use your Application(s).
	5.	“Application(s)” refers to your software programs designed or developed using TEN-VAD or where deployment is enabled by TEN-VAD.

